Plan a phase of work for {{project_name}}.

## Instructions
1. Read the phase scope from project docs
2. Decompose into GitHub Issues with acceptance criteria
3. Assign to team members (FIRSTNAME_LASTNAME labels)
4. Review each issue from multiple perspectives (architecture, devops, data, tech lead, QA, security)
5. Process feedback: update issue descriptions, post replies
6. Propose wave structure with dependencies
7. Present plan to user for approval — do NOT start implementation without approval
